* Select shipping method: Warning! This option disables the merchant calculated shipping. With this option, Google API ignores any attempt to affect shipping prices.
* Izberite način dostave: Opozorilo! Ta možnost trgovcu onemogoči izračun dostave. S to možnostjo Google API ignorira kakršenkoli poskus vpliva na cene dostave.

* Select shipping method: A virtual item to reflect the discount total
* Izberite način dostave: Virtualni element za odraz skupnega popusta

* Select shipping method: A virtual item to reflect the tax total
* Izberite način dostave: Virtualni element za odraz skupnega davka

* Select shipping method: Credit memo has been created automatically
Enable this if your checkout request is too big and being cut off.
* Izberite način dostave: To omogočite, če je vaš zahtevek nakupa prevelik in je odrezan.

* Select shipping method: If enabled, cart contents will be hidden after clicking on the Google Checkout button in the shopping cart, and restored if "Edit Cart" link was activated.
* Izberite način dostave: Če je omogočeno, bo po kliku na gumb Google Checkout vsebina košarice skrita v košarici in obnovljena, če je aktivirana povezava "Uredite košarico".

* Select shipping method: Is Buyer Willing to Receive Marketing Emails: %s
* Izberite način dostave: Ali je kupec pripravljen dobivati marketinško e-pošto: %s
Naslednji dan po zraku zgodaj zjutraj
Naslednji dan po zraku s prihrankom

* Select shipping method: Optional, leave empty for home page.
* Izberite način dostave: Neobvezno, pustite prazno za domačo stran.

* Select shipping method: Required for live Google Checkout transactions. Make sure that this option corresponds to Use Secure URLs in Frontend ("Web" > "Secure").
* Izberite način dostave: Zahtevano za Google Checkout transakcije v živo. Zagotovite, da se ta možnost ujema z uporabo varnih URL-jev v ospredju ("Splet" > "Varnost").

* Select shipping method: The tax amount has been applied based on the information received from Google Checkout, because tax amount received from Google Checkout is different from the calculated tax amount
* Izberite način dostave: Znesek davka je bil uporabljen na osnovi informacij prejetih iz Google Checkout, ker je znesek davka pridobljen iz Google Checkout drugačen od izračunanega zneska davka

* Select shipping method: You will be redirected to GoogleCheckout in a few seconds.
* Izberite način dostave: V nekaj sekundah boste preusmerjeni na GoogleCheckout.
